<h3 id="to-someone-who-has-performed-the-prayer-ṣalāt">
To someone who has performed the prayer (<em>ṣalāt</em>)
</h3>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left">
تقبل الله
</td>
<td align="left">
منّي ومنّك
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td align="left">
<em>taqabbal alla</em>
</td>
<td align="left">
<em>minni u-minnak</em>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left">
May God accept
</td>
<td align="left">
From me and from you
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="asking-someone-to-be-patientcalm-down">
Asking someone to be patient/calm down
</h3>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
