</td>
<td align="left">
الله يصلي عالنبي
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td align="left">
<em>ṣalli ʿa-n-nabi</em>
</td>
<td align="left">
<em>allah yuṣalli ʿa-n-nabi</em>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
